## About Media Enrichments

Media files in this gallery have been analyzed using AI to provide:

- **Context** - When and why the link was shared
- **Summary** - Key points from the content
- **Relevance** - Connection to your conversations

Each enrichment combines the shared URL with AI-generated insights to help you rediscover and understand the resources that mattered to you.
